## Phase 2: Dynamic smoke (smoke_keff_dynamic.py)

Scales cartservice from 1 to 2 replicas. Polls k_eff every 1s under all
three warmup curves to verify the trajectory. T_cold configured as 15s
(C# .NET stack, per config.yaml).

